OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a mostly dry and
OL,6,Fcloudy day across Orkney and Shetland,
OL,7,Fthough there is still a chance of some
OL,8,Fbright or sunny intervals. Light
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA cloudy evening, staying
OL,12,Flargely dry but a little light rain
OL,13,Fpossible. Little change overnight with
OL,14,Fcloudy conditions and the odd spot of
OL,15,Frain. Light northwesterly winds
OL,16,Fbecoming fresh overnight.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FAnother mostly dry and cloudy
OL,19,Fday with a few brief bright intervals
OL,20,Fbreaking through. Moderate to fresh
OL,21,Fnorthwesterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
